<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-563438-1"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-563438-1')">1</a>. I mean, one of them was one of your previous SCPs re-styled as a Nexus.</div>
</div>

